<sect1 renderas="sect2" id="download" label=""><title>Download</title>
<para>
 You can <ulink url="/sf-download-mirror/">download Privoxy here</ulink>,
 from <ulink url="https://www.silvester.org.uk/privoxy/">this mirror</ulink>,
 or from <ulink url="https://sourceforge.net/projects/ijbswa/files/">SourceForge</ulink>.
</para>
<para>
 Note that the Privoxy project currently has no trusted build infrastructure.
 Binary packages are built and uploaded by individual members of the Privoxy
 project or external contributors. For details check the signatures.
</para>
<para>
 Subscribe to the <ulink url="/feeds/privoxy-releases.xml">release feed</ulink>
 to get informed when new releases are available.
</para>
</sect1>

